About this item

  • 【Immerse Yourself into the Music】USB type c headphones with microphone adopt High-definition 40 mm driver and compact earcups design, which deliver clear sound. Effortless style and powerful sound let you tune into your own rhythms with the set of over-ear usb c wired headphones. You can easily use these stereo USB C headphones for your workouts, job commute or just for listening at home
  • 【A touch of Simplicity for Audio Controls】Friendly multifunctional button for making calls,and skipping tracks forward and back. The buttons volume controls of this corded plug in usb c wired headphones allow you to manage phone calls and control music, as simple as few clicks without missing a beat, just enjoy premium music quality and hear ever details whether working in the office, walking outdoors, or on the subway. A pair of headphones that are more suitable for talking
  • 【Designed for Maximum Comfort】Soft padded earcups are comfortable, lightweight, noise-cancelling and can swivel 90 degrees for a compact design. Ultra-soft padded headband provide you a fatigue-free listening experience even wearing these usb c over-ear wired headphones during a long session. Adjustable slider helps you achieve the perfect fit without constraint. You can easily use these stereo headphones for your workouts, job commute or just for listening at home
  • 【Durable & Foldable Design】These wired headphones usb c in bright colors are built meticulously with strong and sturdy plastic and PU leather for long-lasting resilience and durability. Premium 1.5m nylon braiding cord doesn’t tangle or kink, suitable for adults and teens. Lightweight and foldable design make these wired usb c headphones easy to put into your package and take along anywhere which are ideal for easy on the go or travelling
  • 【Hifi Stereo Sound with Wide Compatibility】USB C wired headphone with HD Microphone ensures excellent voice pick-up and automatically suppress wind noise for optimized calls whether you are in work, study or gaming. These over ear usb c headphones with microphone support a wide range of devices like cell phones (iPhone 15/16/17 Series), computers, laptops, tablet other USB-C audio jack devices for gym, listening to music and games. (When connecting headphones, you need to set the inserted device as headphones on the computer/laptops. ) Please note: this USB C wired headphones are not compatible with an ACER Chromebook
  • 【Service Support】Cowyawn offers you 2-year free replacement and lifetime professional technical support. If you have any questions, please contact seller support and we will provide you.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
